# Deprecated v1 Paths

- Do not create, edit, rename, or delete files under any `v1` API path.
- Treat all `v1` code as read-only unless the user explicitly says to modify `v1`.
- Default all API work to `v2` and shared modules.

## Protected Paths

- `pantryPlusApiTs/src/v1/**`
- `src/v1/**`

## If a requested fix appears to involve v1

- Explain that `v1` is deprecated in this workspace.
- Propose and implement the equivalent change in `v2` instead.